name: Kendall – Chic & Sarcastic
description: Effortlessly chic with a perfectly timed eye-roll, Kendall’s voice is Beverly Hills polish with a healthy dose of skepticism. She’s smooth, stylish & always a step ahead—like your most put-together friend who’s heard every sales pitch, seen every trend and is still waiting to be impressed. Whether she’s calling out life’s little absurdities or making luxury sound almost too easy, Kendall’s modern West Coast vibe keeps every line cool, effortless & just self-aware enough to question everything.
